{"tid":1352552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入元朗一定要入 727同我入元朗","createTime":"2019-07-22T20:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T21:32:24.000Z","uid":199606,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38e0d28eb39703f23d02fde1401ff4430851a7b2","tid":1352552,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:19:00.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬係要打但係唔可以自己挑機先<br />\n我地最主要目的一定係五大訴求<br />\n依家主動開人拖不論贏唔贏<br />\n一定會自損 民意 裝備甚至係勇武手足<br />\n<br />\n元朗單野已經令到沉默港豬同淺藍醒覺<br />\n但係佢地係第一次參與社運<br />\n第一次黎就打生打死<br />\n你覺得開拖會令到佢地持續參加社運咩<br />\n我地既目標係五大訴求 元朗只係支線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n727光復元朗係要但唔係要主動開佢拖<br />\n元朗遊行示威反警黑 反白色恐佈 要利用全城恐慌<br />\n要阻止白色恐怖蔓延轉化做我地既力量<br />\n而唔係主動開人拖令到自己變做白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n矛頭係應該對返政府<br />\n元朗黑社會可以贏左政府再清算<br />\n無論元朗一戰贏定輸都對我地不利<br />\n贏左警察都會捉人 黑社會咪最多交咪交幾個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁當然畀人打就一定要還拖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"03889ea704963512d2a626ebee2fc04ab6e5c356","tid":1352552,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:19:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"993f3b1bf96790c9ea4f93a66c2225694343062f","tid":1352552,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:19:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"689e52af92adf6b3f3af71064d2e8370b7462a8c","tid":1352552,"uid":168003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:20:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"12ea629c4a1da36da549b5b43d3724565cfc11a2","tid":1352552,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:55:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e528e9b067355be09ddff3e3a1110d0d5332c4e5","tid":1